Class DAABB

java.lang.Object
  org.ode4j.ode.DAABB
All Implemented Interfaces:
DAABBC
public class DAABB
extends java.lang.Object
implements DAABBC

Convenience class for operations on AABB (Axis-aligned bounding boxes).

Axes are numbered from 0 to 2.

Author:
Tilmann Zaeschke
See Also:
